ANNOTATION_NOTES: Radif 'چاہتا ہوں' consistently appears. Qaafiya follows الف and ا endings. Famous ghazal seeking the limit of divine love.
Radif 'چھوڑ دے'. Long philosophical ghazal on complete renunciation. When Majnun left city, leave desert too.
Radif 'کر'. Make radiant tresses more radiant. Beauty is flame-scattering.
Radif 'میں'. O awaited reality, appear in garb of metaphor. Famous opening couplet.
Compound radif 'پیدا کر'. Come out of arena, create earth or sky. Self-assertion theme.
Radif 'ہے'. Desert ruby not mere color, essence is stone. Pain is essence of humanity.
Radif 'ہے'. Do not think intellect and heart are merely names. Love is essence, intellect its veil.
Radif 'نے'. Storm of West made Muslim into Muslim. Turbulence of sea gives pearl lustre.
Compound radif 'رکھتی ہے'. Whatever emerges from heart has effect, though lacks power of flight.
Radif 'تھا'. O young Muslim, did he ever contemplate? Famous poem on Muslim identity.
Radif 'نہیں'. Love is a reality, no doubt. That is not love which is merely a tale.
Radif 'ہے'. From action, life is made—both heaven and hell. Earthly being neither light nor fire.
Radif 'جا'. Break idols of color and blood, become lost in nation. Let no Turanian, Iranian, Afghan remain.
Radif 'ہے'. Stability of life through firm faith. Turanian more lasting than German.
Radif 'ہے'. Vision of Abraham born with difficulty. Desire hides in hearts creating images.
Radif 'ہے'. Proof of bright dawn is faint light of stars. Sun risen, age of heavy sleep gone.
Radif 'ہے'. This new age is heartless, talk of love. Neither bulbul knows, nor bud has song.
Radif 'چھوڑے'. Tell Persia to abandon spring. Leave us with our tulip and rose intoxication.
Radif 'نہیں'. Love is limitless ocean with no shore. Intellect is captain unaware of this ocean.
Radif 'کی'. Gaze of longing excavated wall of sanctuary. Muslim's gaze changes destinies.
Radif 'ہے'. New dawn gave message: self-observant man should never flee. Life is self-nurturing.
Radif 'ہے'. I am stranger in city, listen to my cry. In your breast too, wonders reside.
Radif 'ہے'. Self-awareness taught self-forgetfulness. He who knows art of independence is dervish.
Radif 'کی'. O region of flowers, no need for explanation. Image on heart is tulip of blood.
Radif 'ہے'. West's conscience mercantile, East's monastic. There changes moment by moment, here time does not change.
Radif 'آور'. Bring that high resolve, bring that passion of liver. If you seek father's sword, bring father's arm.
Radif 'ہے'. He created essence of humanity, gave knowledge of whole world. By His glory world is inhabited.
Radif 'ہے'. He is moving bird whose nest is neither East nor West. Man of God sees no Kaaba, no temple.
Radif 'نہیں'. No bond except love. Love of Muhammad is recognition of selfhood.
No consistent radif. Desire in heart to be of use. Life needs purpose.
Radif 'قائم'. Bond of love established from eternity, will never break.
Radif 'سے'. Iqbal not hopeless of desolate cultivation. Soil fertile with moisture.
No consistent radif. Sovereign in world who needs art. Muslim's gaze changes destinies.
Radif 'ہے'. Knowledge plentiful but lifeless. Knowledge with action flows.
Radif 'ہے'. Love where life is staked, no fear for life. Selfhood secret of universe.
Radif 'ہے'. Complaint of age's blind taste. My labor thought to be Farhad's.
Radif 'ہے'. Muslim man is God's servant, needs none other. Age thinks Iqbal poet, not dervish.
Radif 'کی'. Do not hope for fidelity from world's wealth. Muslim identity is acknowledging Allah.
Single couplet with radif 'آشکارا'. Secret of enslaved nations: earth can break house's confinement.
Radif 'ہے'. Iqbal's call: destination far, paths remain. He created essence of humanity.
Radif 'ہے'. From Your radiance world gains prosperity. There is none but You.
Radif 'ہے'. In presence of Beloved, book of conversation opened. No difference between living and dying in love.
Radif 'ہے'. Love is essence of life, intellect its veil. People of certainty attain success.
No consistent radif. New moon passed beyond every station. Who attained perfection without struggle?
Radif 'کی'. He exists who protected selfhood. Stages of love are something else.
Radif 'تھی'. Your ancient being existed from eternity. Flower adorned garden, fragrance not scattered.
Radif 'بھی'. Someone used to take Your name. Here dwelt Seljuqs and Turanians too.
Radif 'تھے'. We were among those in Your battlefields. Died for Your name's greatness.
Compound radif 'کس نے'. Who broke idols? Who cooled fire-temple of Iran?
Radif 'ہوئے'. In one row stood Mahmud and Ayaz. No master remained, no servant remained.
Compound radif 'ہم نے'. We erased falsehood from page of time. Yet You complain we are not loyal.
Radif 'ہیں'. Among them lazy, heedless, vigilant. Lightning falls on poor Muslims.
Radif 'نہیں'. No complaint their treasures full. Infidel gets houris, Muslim only promise.
Radif 'ہے'. Taunt of rivals, disgrace, poverty. We live that Your name remains.
Radif 'گئے'. Your assembly gone, lovers gone. Night's sighs gone, morning's laments gone.
Radif 'وہی'. Love's heart the same, beauty's magic the same. Community of Ahmad the same, You the same.
Radif 'ہے'. We keep fire of Allahu Akbar hidden. Love's former style no more.
Compound radif 'تو نے'. On Mount Faran, You perfected religion. With one gesture, won thousands of hearts.
Compound radif 'نہ رہا'. Those aspirations no more, we no more, heart no more. House ruined.
Radif 'کر دے'. Wandering nation turns to Hejaz. Make rare commodity of love abundant.
Radif 'چمن'. Make love abundant, temple-dwellers into Muslims. Flowers are informers of garden.
Compound radif 'اب تک'. One nightingale remains absorbed in song. Its breast has turbulence of melodies.
Radif 'ہے'. Pleasure in dying, not living. Essences restless in mirror.
Radif 'ہے'. If vessel Persian, my wine Hejazi. My power of speech taught audacity.
Radif 'ہے'. Instruments silent, we filled with lament. Listen to complaint of faithful.
Radif 'تھی'. We had restlessness of heart. Before us, stones worshipped, trees adored.
Duplicate of iqbal_00113. Radif 'بھی'. Someone used to take Your name.
Duplicate of iqbal_00114. Radif 'تھے'. We were among those in Your battlefields.
Radif 'تھے'. Our nation died for world's wealth. In battle, we would fly.
Partial of iqbal_00115. Compound radif 'کس نے'. Who uprooted door of Khaybar?
Radif 'ہوئی'. Whose sword world-conquering became world-ruling? By whose cry did Your world awaken?
Duplicate of iqbal_00116. Radif 'ہوئے'. In one row stood Mahmud and Ayaz.
Duplicate of iqbal_00119. Radif 'نہیں'. Disbelief laughs, do you feel?
Radif 'ہے'. Why wealth rare among Muslims? Your power has no limit.
Partial of iqbal_00121. Radif 'گئے'. We departed, others took over world. Your assembly gone.
Compound radif 'لے کر'. Lovers came and went taking promise of tomorrow. Search with lamp.
Radif 'چھوڑا'. We left You? Left Arab Messenger? Made idol-worship profession?
Radif 'سہی'. Restless heart like compass no more. Sometimes with us, sometimes strangers.
Partial of iqbal_00125. Compound radif 'نہ رہا'. Why breasts not filled with sparks?
Radif 'دے'. Away from garden clamor, they sit. Give moths desire for self-immolation.
Partial of iqbal_00126. Radif 'کر دے'. Melodies restless to emerge. Make love abundant.
Radif 'چمن'. Scent of flower carried garden's secret. Era of roses ended.
Radif 'کی'. Nature free from imprisonment of seasons. Pleasure in dying, not living.
Radif 'ہوں'. Hearts revived by new era of fidelity. If vessel Persian, wine Hejazi.
Radif 'ہے'. Power of speech taught audacity. Instruments silent, we filled with lament.
Duplicate of iqbal_00132. Radif 'تھی'. Condition of justice: how would scent spread without breeze?
Radif 'تھے'. Glory of world-rulers didn't fit our eyes. If we lived, for wars we lived.
Radif 'تھے'. If anyone rebellious, we would be enraged. We impressed monotheism on every heart.
Duplicate of iqbal_00137. Radif 'ہوئی'. Which nation became Your seeker?
Radif 'ہے'. We populated Kaaba with foreheads. Yet You complain we are not loyal.
Radif 'پر'. Your mercies on rivals' houses. Lightning falls on poor Muslims.
Partial of iqbal_00142. Radif 'ہے'. If You wish, bubbles rise from desert.
Radif 'ہے'. We live that Your name remains. Your assembly gone, lovers gone.
Partial of iqbal_00122. Radif 'وہی'. Pain of Laila same, manner of Qais same.
Duplicate of iqbal_00145. Radif 'چھوڑا'. Left love, left madness of love.
Radif 'بیٹھے'. Wine-drinkers strangers in garden. Away from clamor, they sit.
Partial of iqbal_00150. Radif 'چمن'. Era of roses ended, garden's instrument broke.
Radif 'بھی'. Before us strange scene in Your world. Here dwelt Seljuqs and Turanians too.
Radif 'کس نے'. But who raised sword for Your name? We gave calls to prayer in Europe's churches.
Radif 'تھے'. Our sword-fighting not for rule. We would not retreat, in battle fly.
Radif 'تھے'. By whose awe idols terrified? If prayer time in battle, bowed to earth.
Duplicate of iqbal_00118. Radif 'ہیں'. Other communities, sinners too.
Radif 'چھوڑا'. Then what this displeasure without reason? We left You?
Radif 'نہ رہا'. In valley of Najd, clamor of chains no more. Wine-drinkers strangers in garden.
Radif 'ما'. Stream of blood from ancient longing. Scent carried garden's secret.
Radif 'ہے'. Old ways of garden desolate. Branches bare of leaves.
Duplicate of iqbal_00171. Radif 'ہوں'. I am hearts torn by nightingale's song.
Radif 'نہیں'. In temples, idols say Muslims gone. Disbelief laughs, do you feel?
Radif 'ہیں'. Beyond stars, more worlds. You are falcon, flight your destiny.
